extendedInfo.description: If you are Attack Attack!'s fan, this app is right for you. Whenever you want to check Attack Attack!'s lyrics, just open this app and choose the lyrics that you want. You don't have to access the internet to get the lyrics. We provide all Attack Attack!'s lyrics here. In the Album tab, you can choose lyrics based on the album. In All lyrics tab, all of Attack Attack!'s lyrics are here. You can quickly search the lyrics by using the search bar at the top of the page.Hope you guy enjoy using this app as much as I enjoy developing it. :)-------------------------------- Main Features -------------------------------- - Lyrics categorized by album - Show all lyrics - Search lyrics-------------------------------- List of albums -------------------------------- - Someday Came Suddenly- Attack Attack!- This Means War-------------------------------- List of lyrics -------------------------------- - A For Andrew- AC-130- All Alone- Bro, Ashley's Here- Catfish Soup- Criminal- Dr. Shavargo Pt. 3- Fumbles O'Brian- Hot Grills, And High Tops- I Swear, I'll Change- Kickin' Wing, Animal Doctor- Last Breath- Lonely- Party Foul- Pick A Side- Renob, Nevada- Sexual Man Chocolate- Shred, White, And Blue- Shut Your Mouth- Smokahontas- Stick Stickly- The Abduction- The Betrayal- The Confrontation- The Eradication- The Family- The Hopeless- The Motivation- The People's Elbow- The Reality- The Revolution- The Wretched- Turbo Swag- What Happens If I Can't Check My Myspace When We Get There?
